{
  "id": "class_0061",
  "name": "Exiled Court Scribe",
  "title_completion": "an Exiled Court Scribe",
  "flavor_text": "Once, your quill gave the Mad King's ravings the weight of law \u2014 now the edicts you inscribed hunt you across the wind-scoured realm. You wield neither sword nor sorcery, only the terrible authority of words written in haste and sealed in blood. The throne room remembers your handwriting, and so do its marble walls, which shudder when you speak.",
